<p>The investment is 4 to 6 hours per week of genuine participation. The return is diversified, algorithm-resistant visibility that traditional SEO alone cannot provide.</p>
<p>Start with your profile. Find 3 topic clusters. Answer 3 to 5 questions per week. Track your results. And let the compounding begin.</p>
